install docker 
---------------------
Pull Jenkins image from docker hub.
Command: docker pull Jenkins/Jenkins
----------------------------------
Inspect the ports exposed by container/image.
Command:#docker inspect image_id
Example:#docker inspect db75aa81ca2b
-----------------------------------
Run the docker Jenkins image along with data port and control port.
Command:docker run -p 4899:8080 -p 50000:50000 jenkins/Jenkins
** remember to copy the password of jenkins**
-------------------------------------
Expose Jenkins image with data port.
copy public IP of EC2 and paste along with data port paste on browser
*data port number is :4899
----------------------------------------
Expose Jenkins image with control port.
copy public IP of EC2 and paste along with control port paste on browser
*control port number is :50000 
